name: Online Food Dataset
data_intro: The dataset contains information collected from an online food ordering platform over a period of time. It encompasses various attributes related to Occupation, Family Size, Feedback etc..

cat_feature_intro.Marital Status: Marital Status: Marital status of the customer.
cat_feature_intro.Monthly Income: Monthly Income: Monthly income of the customer.
cat_feature_intro.Educational Qualifications: Educational Qualifications: Educational qualifications of the customer.
cat_feature_intro.Output: Output: Current status of the order (e.g., pending, confirmed, delivered).
cat_feature_intro.Feedback: This dataset can be utilized to explore the relationship between demographic/location factors and online food ordering behavior, analyze customer feedback to improve service quality, and potentially predict customer preferences or behavior based on demographic and location attributes.

num_feature_intro.Family size: Family Size: Number of individuals in the customer's family.
num_feature_intro.latitude: Latitude: Latitude of the customer's location.
num_feature_intro.longitude: Longitude: Longitude of the customer's location.
num_feature_intro.Pin code: Pin Code: Pin code of the customer's location.
